title: Yuka Honda (Of Cibo Matto) Studio Discography
description:
None of these are my rips but I couldn't find all of her albums together in one place so I compiled all of her albums post Cibo Matto in flac into one torrent
I was going to include Miho Hatori's solo album as well but I couldn't find it in flac and there's already a 320 rip up so I didn't bother

Includes:
Butter 08 - Butter 08
Yuka Honda - Memories Are My Only Witness
Yoshimi And Yuka - Flower With No Color
Yuka Honda - Eucademix
Yuka Honda - Heart Chamber Phantoms
If By Yes - Salt On Sea Glass

If you like the music please buy it and support the artist
